{"tid":1786991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【甴總訪澳前夕】獲官方確認可採訪慶回歸活動　南早記者仍被拒入境澳門","createTime":"2019-12-17T14:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T11:03:23.000Z","uid":21141,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8edf3b38b048f99f025823e789cd84760d4c60e4","tid":1786991,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:32:27.000Z","msg":"繼《Now 新聞台》記者，昨日經港珠澳大橋到澳門採訪，被大陸邊檢人員拒絕入境後，《南華早報》一名已向澳門當局登記，並確認可以採訪習近平訪澳行程的記者，今日乘船抵達澳門外港碼頭時被扣查問話，最終經近 3 小時後他被拒入境，警方指有明顯跡象顯示，他有可能危害澳門社會秩序和公共安全。<br />\n《南華早報》引述總編輯譚衛兒指，對事件感極度遺憾，涉事記者和其他《南華早報》記者不會對任何地區帶來安全風險，記者今次的遭遇完全不合理。<br />\n<br />\n《南華早報》報道，該報記者蕭志鋭上星期曾到澳門採訪，當時經兩小時問話後獲准入境；星期一晚他收到澳門政府通知，可以在星期二到澳門領取慶回歸活動的採訪證，但他下午約 1 時半乘船抵達澳門外港碼頭，隨即被截查和帶到一間房間問話，當局要求他提供住址、家人姓名、婚姻狀況等個人資料，和交代到澳門的原因，記者亦有出示他在澳門的酒店預訂紀錄和採訪邀請等，警方亦問他除了採訪慶回歸活動外，有沒有計劃採訪其他人，記者回答無。<br />\n最終經近三小時扣查問話，當局拒絕蕭志鋭入境，指他有可能危害澳門社會秩序和公共安全，他隨即獲安全上船返回香港。<br />\n<br />\nSouce:<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%A8%AA%E6%BE%B3%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%95-%E7%8D%B2%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E6%85%B6%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E5%8D%97%E6%97%A9%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E4%BB%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A4%2595-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%2585%25B6%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BB%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=eb6ac6a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25A4%2595-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%2585%25B6%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BB%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F&h=c84988b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%A8%AA%E6%BE%B3%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%95-%E7%8D%B2%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E6%85%B6%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E5%8D%97%E6%97%A9%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E4%BB%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/</a><br />\n<br />\n黑記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93dd96bdb7e89829afb23fa4c17ffa50134e01b5","tid":1786991,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"c4e932d0ba64bbaa3242efddc5040d20e5fe5c78","tid":1786991,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"金融忠心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}